he's pushing around
the millions who voted for you.

1059
01:10:17,120 --> 01:10:18,997
Well, not quite that many.

1060
01:10:19,120 --> 01:10:21,076
How many, then?

1061
01:10:21,680 --> 01:10:24,831
Eight hundred and sixty-three thousand,
four hundred and thirty-four.

1062
01:10:24,960 --> 01:10:28,396
