Don't start up with him.

1073
01:11:18,480 --> 01:11:20,152
They're legit.

1074
01:11:20,280 --> 01:11:22,874
Why can't I read them, then?
There must be something wrong...

1075
01:11:23,000 --> 01:11:24,672
They're all right!

1076
01:11:28,160 --> 01:11:30,116
I'm sorry.

1077
01:11:31,480 --> 01:11:33,357
It's OK, I understand.

1078
01:11:33,480 --> 01:11:35,994
