1082
01:11:48,440 --> 01:11:50,396
Maybe you're worse.

1083
01:12:04,400 --> 01:12:06,356
"Pursuant."

1084
01:12:10,160 --> 01:12:12,116
Good word.

1085
01:12:30,320 --> 01:12:32,276
What's the matter?

1086
01:12:33,400 --> 01:12:34,879
Ed.

1087
01:12:35,920 --> 01:12:37,797
What'd he do to you?

1088
01:12:37,920 --> 01:12:40,388
It's what he's done to himself.

1089
01:12:40,520 --> 01:12:44,274
Do you know, he used to be
attorney general of a whole state?

1090
01:12:44,400 --> 01:12:46,072
Do you know, he wrote a book?

1091
01:12:46,200 --> 01:12:50,239
It was called <i>The Roots of Freedom.</i>
I read it. It was beautiful.

1092
01:12:50,360 --> 01:12:52,749
Don't tie up your new brain with Ed.

1093
01:12:56,360 --> 01:12:58,749
You're not as big as I used to think.

1094
01:12:59,760 --> 01:13:02,991
All through history,
there's been bigger men and better.

1095
01:13:03,760 --> 01:13:05,716
Name somebody bigger.

1096
01:13:08,080 --> 01:13:10,150
My father.

1097
01:13:10,280 --> 01:13:11,872
Minimum wage!

1098
01:13:12,000 --> 01:13:14,798
So what? At least he spent time with me.

1099
01:13:14,920 --> 01:13:19,471
- I work every day. Even Sundays.
- For what, for who...? For whom?

1100
01:13:19,600 --> 01:13:22,353
For money!
What do you think?

1101
01:13:22,480 --> 01:13:24,835
So go rob a bank! That's work!

1102
01:13:25,720 --> 01:13:28,439
I have never in my whole life...

1103
01:13:31,960 --> 01:13:33,473
...robbed a bank!

1104
01:13:33,600 --> 01:13:35,511
You're still not big.

1105
01:13:35,640 --> 01:13:38,313
You don't care about anything big.

1106
01:13:38,440 --> 01:13:41,591
Don't get nervous
just cos you read a book.

1107
01:13:41,720 --> 01:13:44,314
You're still as dumb as you ever were.

1108
01:13:44,440 --> 01:13:47,591
But I don't mind,
cos you're still the hottest little...

1109
01:13:47,720 --> 01:13:49,358
Come here!

1110
01:13:50,400 --> 01:13:54,439
