1115
01:14:13,680 --> 01:14:16,638
You got money, Harry,
but you got a cheap life.

1116
01:14:16,760 --> 01:14:19,718
I don't own nothin' cheap
except you.

1117
01:14:19,840 --> 01:14:23,116
